    "attributes": {
        "action": "Require credit rating agencies to provide a way to wipe bad credit records",
        "additional_details": "Giving everyone the opportunity to start fresh means everyone will get a chance and all be in it together to kick start the economy. A lot of individuals have got bad credit and great ideas. People with bad credit are getting mentally sick feeling depressed and feeling like a nobody as there is no route for them. Covid-19 will and already has affected a lot of people.\r\n\r\nWe need to be in this together and support each other.\r\n",
        "background": "The Government should regulate credit rating agencies to ensure that there is an accessible way for all people to clear their bad credit history. ",
